LIKE A PIG. I'M JUST SAYING‐‐
OH, I THOUGHT
THAT'S WHAT YOU WERE SAYING!

00:41:06,998 --> 00:41:11,402
NO, I'M SAYING YOU WOULD LOOK
ADORABLE AS A REAL‐LIFE MASCOT.
(Daymond) YEAH.

00:41:11,402 --> 00:41:14,472
I GUESS I'LL TAKE THAT
AS A COMPLIMENT.
IT'S A COMPLIMENT.

00:41:14,472 --> 00:41:18,810
I DON'T KNOW HOW ELSE
YOU CAN TAKE IT.
ONLY A POLITICIAN WOULD
TAKE THAT AS A COMPLIMENT!

00:41:18,810 --> 00:41:21,879
YOU KNOW, UM, ACTUALLY
I'M INTERESTED IN YOUR BUSINESS.

00:41:21,879 --> 00:41:24,215
BUT, OF COURSE,
THE NUMBERS ARE CRAZY.

00:41:24,215 --> 00:41:25,883
WHAT ABOUT THE $50,000?

00:41:25,883 --> 00:41:28,619
I DON'T SEE THAT AS A LOT OF
MONEY TO PRODUCE MUCH PRODUCT.

00:41:28,619 --> 00:41:32,957
WHAT HAPPENS WHEN
THE $50,000 RUNS OUT?

00:41:32,957 --> 00:41:35,727
I THINK THE‐‐THE REVENUE
THAT WE'LL GENERATE,

00:41:35,727 --> 00:41:38,196
PLUS WE ACTUALLY HAVE ANOTHER
$100,000 OF OUR OWN MONEY

00:41:38,196 --> 00:41:41,766
THAT WE'RE PREPARED TO INVEST.
OH, REALLY?

00:41:41,766 --> 00:41:44,702
WE'RE VERY COMMITTED TO THIS.
THIS IS NOT A HOBBY.

00:41:44,702 --> 00:41:47,205
BARBARA, ARE YOU MAKING
AN OFFER?
I AM.

00:41:47,205 --> 00:41:48,940
THE OFFER IS

00:41:48,940 --> 00:41:52,443
I'LL BE HAPPY TO GIVE YOU
THE $50,000, ALL RIGHT?

00:41:52,443 --> 00:41:54,579
BUT FOR 50% OF THE BUSINESS.

00:41:54,579 --> 00:41:57,515
WOULD YOU BE WILLING TO DO
40% AND A PIG COSTUME?

00:41:57,515 --> 00:41:58,750
(laughs)

00:42:02,220 --> 00:42:04,355
NO.

00:42:04,355 --> 00:42:07,592
YOU'RE VERY LUCKY
I WASN'T ASKING FOR 51%.

00:42:12,864 --> 00:42:15,633
WE'D LOVE TO ACCEPT
YOUR OFFER.

00:42:15,633 --> 00:42:17,802
ARE YOU WITH HIM ON THAT?
I'M WITH HIM ON THAT.

00:42:17,802 --> 00:42:20,071
YOU'VE GOT A DEAL.
GREAT.

00:42:20,071 --> 00:42:22,306
YOU'VE GOT
A GREAT SENSE OF HUMOR.
THANK YOU VERY MUCH.

00:42:22,306 --> 00:42:25,043
THANK YOU SO MUCH.
(kisses cheek)

00:42:25,043 --> 00:42:28,446
(laughs) THANK YOU. THANK YOU
SO MUCH. (kisses cheek)
WE LOOK FORWARD TO THIS.

00:42:30,281 --> 00:42:33,618
YOU KNOW, THE TRUTH IS,
HE DOESN'T EVEN NEED A COSTUME.

00:42:33,618 --> 00:42:36,921
HE JUST NEEDS THE EARS.
I DIDN'T CALL‐‐NO, NOT AT ALL.
YOU JUST CALLED HIM A PIG
ON NATIONAL TV.

00:42:36,921 --> 00:42:39,924
(O'Leary) I THINK YOU DID.
I THINK YOU DID, YEAH.
I DID NOT.

00:42:39,924 --> 00:42:42,427
WE WENT INTO THE TANK
FACING FIVE SHARKS.

00:42:42,427 --> 00:42:45,596
IN THE END, THERE WAS
ONE SHARK STANDING...
AND ONE PIG.

00:42:45,596 --> 00:42:48,800
BUT, YOU KNOW,
WE'RE SO EXCITED WE GOT A DEAL.

00:42:55,373 --> 00:42:57,375
