<i>EPISODE OF "SHARK TANK"</i>

00:42:57,375 --> 00:42:59,577
<i>ON ITS NEW NIGHT AND TIME‐‐</i>

00:42:59,577 --> 00:43:02,313
<i>TUESDAY, SEPTEMBER 29th</i>
<i>AT 8:00 P. M.</i>

00:43:02,313 --> 00:43:04,315
I'M THE WORLD'S
MOST ACCURATE KNIFE THROWER.
WOW.

00:43:04,315 --> 00:43:06,717
MOMMY!
YOU ARE NUTS, DAYMOND.

00:43:06,717 --> 00:43:09,220
EDWIN, ARE YOU A VAMPIRE?

00:43:09,220 --> 00:43:12,323
ENOUGH CHATTER.
LET'S DO IT.

00:43:12,323 --> 00:43:14,892
LET ME SWEETEN MY OFFER.
WE ALL KNOW KEVIN'S DEAL
IS A WASTE OF TIME.

00:43:14,892 --> 00:43:17,061
NO, IT ISN'T.
YOU'RE OUT.

00:43:17,061 --> 00:43:19,764
NO, NO, I'M NOT FINISHED.
I WOULDN'T TAKE HIS OFFER.

00:43:19,764 --> 00:43:21,799
NOISE! NOISE!
YOU'RE LIKE
HIGH SCHOOL BOYS‐‐

00:43:21,799 --> 00:43:24,769
BARBARA, I'M OFFENDED
BY YOUR SEXISM.

